  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**计数器** \n",
    "\n",
    "hash结构还可以当成计数器来使用，对于内部的每一个key都可以作为独立的计数器。\n",
    "\n",
    "如果value值不是整数，调用hincrby指令会出错。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 15,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "\"40\"\n",
      "(integer) 60\n",
      "\"60\"\n",
      "(integer) 1\n",
      "(error) ERR wrong number of arguments for 'hincrby' command\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1 hget website googleAge \n",
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1 hincrby website googleAge 20 \n",
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1 hget website googleAge \n",
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1 hset website googleName google\n",
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1 hincrby website googleName "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**归纳Hash相关的常用命令**\n",
    "\n",
    "- HSET：将key对应的Hash中的field设置为value。如果该Hash不存在，会自动创建一个。时间复杂度O(1)\n",
    "\n",
    "- HGET：返回指定Hash中field字段的值，时间复杂度O(1)\n",
    "\n",
    "- HMSET/HMGET：同HSET和HGET，可以批量操作同一个key下的多个field，时间复杂度：O(N)，N为一次操作的field数量\n",
    "\n",
    "- HSETNX：同HSET，但如field已经存在，HSETNX不会进行任何操作，时间复杂度O(1)\n",
    "\n",
    "- HEXISTS：判断指定Hash中field是否存在，存在返回1，不存在返回0，时间复杂度O(1)\n",
    "\n",
    "- HDEL：删除指定Hash中的field（1个或多个），时间复杂度：O(N)，N为操作的field数量\n",
    "\n",
    "- HINCRBY：同INCRBY命令，对指定Hash中的一个field进行INCRBY，时间复杂度O(1)\n",
    "\n",
    "应谨慎使用的Hash相关命令：\n",
    "\n",
    "- HGETALL：返回指定Hash中所有的field-value对。返回结果为数组，数组中field和value交替出现。时间复杂度O(N)\n",
    "\n",
    "- HKEYS/HVALS：返回指定Hash中所有的field/value，时间复杂度O(N)\n",
    "\n",
    "上述三个命令都会对Hash进行完整遍历，Hash中的field数量与命令的耗时线性相关，对于尺寸不可预知的Hash，\n",
    "应严格避免使用上面三个命令，而改为使用HSCAN命令进行游标式的遍历，\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### set （集合）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Redis的集合，它内部的键值对是无序的唯一的。\n",
    "\n",
    "它的内部实现相当于一个特殊的字典，字典中所有的 value 都是一个值NULL。\n",
    "\n",
    "当集合中最后一个元素移除之后，数据结构自动删除，内存被回收。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**增加元素**\n",
    "\n",
    "可以一次增加多个元素"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 22,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "(integer) 1\n",
      "(integer) 0\n",
      "(integer) 2\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1  SADD bbs \"discuz.net\"\n",
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1  SADD bbs \"discuz.net\"\n",
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1  SADD bbs \"tianya.cn\" \"groups.google.com\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**读取元素**  \n",
    "\n",
    "使用smembers列出所有元素\n",
    "\n",
    "使用scard获取集合长度\n",
    "\n",
    "使用srandmember获取随机count个元素，如果不提供count参数，默认为1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 23,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "1) \"tianya.cn\"\n",
      "2) \"discuz.net\"\n",
      "3) \"groups.google.com\"\n",
      "(integer) 3\n",
      "\"groups.google.com\"\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1  SMEMBERS bbs \n",
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1  SCARD bbs \n",
    "!redis-cli -h 127.0.0.1  SRANDMEMBER bbs "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**删除元素**\n",
    "\n",
    "使用srem删除一到多个元素\n",
    "\n",
    "使用spop删除随机一个元素"
   ]
